{"tid":88976,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[急事求救]連登有無教小朋友既專家？","createTime":"2017-01-21T04:37:42.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-21T07:03:30.000Z","uid":7775,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"17c23f2645b4cf8198a889bc65edc0b673c48f87","tid":88976,"uid":7775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T04:37:42.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n<br />\n小弟工餘有做開義工，逢星期六就去幫尼泊爾小朋友做功課輔導<br />\n<br />\n咁當中就有一位小朋友，比較沉厚寡言<br />\n<br />\n佢自己唔識d功課，我想教佢<br />\n<br />\n但用心教完佢又唔聽<br />\n<br />\n我用引導式問題佢只會答don't know<br />\n有時仲淨係擰下頭<br />\n<br />\n原來係想我直接畀答案佢，甚至幫佢做埋<br />\n<br />\n想請教下巴絲依種情況可以點樣處理？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc1fb2a9e58917f33a09488b6906daefa2a7740f","tid":88976,"uid":31748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T04:46:02.000Z","msg":"真乖"},{"pid":"773a1c27d9056d57ca4e8b0af8b0702fd282ff80","tid":88976,"uid":66355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T04:47:21.000Z","msg":"唔好俾答案 鼓勵佢答左 你再對 如果佢乜都唔寫你直接俾答案 佢就會覺得佢真係乜都唔洗做 <br />\n<br />\n佢如果鳩做 就擦晒佢 要佢改正 點都唔好比答案佢 令佢自己明鳩做仲浪費時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d680de6505ea5f5dd0f5ed86f4ae7735b7a0fc4","tid":88976,"uid":7775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T04:52:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔好俾答案 鼓勵佢答左 你再對 如果佢乜都唔寫你直接俾答案 佢就會覺得佢真係乜都唔洗做 <br />\n<br />\n佢如果鳩做 就擦晒佢 要佢改正 點都唔好比答案佢 令佢自己明鳩做仲浪費時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢真係會乜柒都唔寫<br />\n<br />\n對住本作業坐喺度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98ed2f6a8353233fc32db19e9304070ed0c617aa","tid":88976,"uid":30678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T04:54:58.000Z","msg":"你再唔做功課我就打電話搵你老母"},{"pid":"5be62b2d326a71cb5666722ae0507b914777da87"